&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Logout:&lt;/b&gt; There are two ways to log out of your account.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you are logged in as a returning customer, click on the Not You? link or on the Logout link located in the top right corner of our homepage to go back to the login page..&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Close your web browser window that is displaying the ATG Store webpage to automatically log out.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you have lost your password, select the "forgot your password"&amp;#160;link to retrieve your password.&lt;/p&gt;

