&lt;li&gt;Type in a product name (such as &lt;strong&gt;Sweden End Table&lt;/strong&gt;) and hit the enter key.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Items matching your &lt;strong&gt;search&lt;/strong&gt; words will display.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;To narrow your &lt;strong&gt;search&lt;/strong&gt; further, select a listing under Price Size or Color and hit the enter key.&lt;/li&gt;
