&lt;p&gt;Following is&amp;#160;general information about taking care of your Home Furnishing/Accessories that you purchase from the ATG Store:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#1" target="_self"&gt;Clocks&lt;/a&gt;&amp;#160;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#2" target="_self"&gt;Radios&lt;/a&gt;&amp;#160;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#3" target="_self"&gt;Cushions &amp;amp; Pillows&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#4" target="_self"&gt;Glassware&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#5" target="_self"&gt;Lamps &amp;amp; Lighting&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#6" target="_self"&gt;Decor&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="FONT-WEIGHT: bold"&gt;Clocks &lt;A name="1"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Clocks are delicate items and cleaning should be confined to the exterior of the clock case. &amp;#160;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p style="FONT-WEIGHT: bold"&gt;Radios &lt;a name="2"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Radios&amp;#160;are not waterproof. Use a soft, dry cloth to clean your radio.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p style="FONT-WEIGHT: bold"&gt;Cushions &amp;amp; Pillows&lt;a name="3"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Follow your manufacturers instructions for cleaning the pillows and cushions. Not all items are machine washable and may require dry cleaning.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p style="FONT-WEIGHT: bold"&gt;Glassware &lt;a name="4"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style="FONT-WEIGHT: normal"&gt;Most glassware is fragile. We recommend that you hand-wash the glassware that you purchase from the ATG Store.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="FONT-WEIGHT: bold"&gt;Lamps &amp;amp; Lighting&lt;a name="5"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style="FONT-WEIGHT: normal"&gt;Bulbs are not included in the lamps packaging from the ATG Store. You need to purchase the bulbs separately and ensure that you follow the manufacturers instructions for purchasing the right type of bulb.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="FONT-WEIGHT: bold"&gt;Decor&lt;a name="6"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Follow the manufacturers instructions for taking care of the decorative items you purchase from the ATG Store.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Standard Shipping:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;a name="1"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;ATG Store &amp;amp; ATG Home&amp;#160;offers various shipping methods and each one comes with its own associated price.&amp;#160;Shipping applies to most destinations within the contiguous United States (excluding Hawaii and Alaska)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Orders ship within 1-3 business days and should arrive within 5-10 business days.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We use all major mail carriers, including UPS, FedEx, and the United States Postal Service. Customers cannot specify the carrier of their choice.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Alaska and Hawaii Shipping:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;a name="2"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Due to carrier restrictions, we cannot ship some items to Alaska and Hawaii.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;APO/FPO Shipping:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;a name="3"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;APO/FPO/DPO(Army Post Office/Fleet Post Office/Diplomatic Post Office)addresses are for U.S. military/government personnel stationed overseas.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We usually deliver these orders to the US military post office within 5-10 business days.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;P.O. Box Shipping:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;a name="4"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If we cannot ship an item to a P.O. Box, we will ask you to provide a physical shipping address.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Expedited shipping is not available for items shipped to P.O. boxes or APO/FPO addresses.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;International and US Territory Shipping:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;a name="6"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are continually expanding our shipping services to additional countries.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Some products may not be eligible for international shipping.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;ATG Store&amp;#160;customers cannot ship to international destinations at this time.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We do not currently ship to US Territories.&lt;/p&gt;

