&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Shipping and Delivery Information&lt;/b&gt;&lt;a name="1"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Fragile items&amp;#160;leave our warehouse within 1-10 business days.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We cannot ship&amp;#160;fragile items to rural routes, Hawaii and Alaska, APO/FPO addresses, or P.O. boxes.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If we can arrange to deliver&amp;#160;fragile items to a remote or isolated area not commonly serviced by freight carriers, delivery may take an additional 1-2 weeks and may incur a fee.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Fragile&amp;#160;items arrive directly to your shipping address via a freight carrier.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The carrier will use the phone numbers you provide during checkout to contact you 24-48 hours prior to delivery to arrange a delivery time. (Available delivery times vary depending on the freight carrier's schedule.)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our freight carriers provide&amp;#160;fragile standard delivery service unless a "White Glove Delivery" notation is on the product page&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Delivery time for most&amp;#160;fragile items is 1-6 weeks from the shipping date.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Inspect the delivery carton for any damage, crushing, dents, creasing, etc. before signing the delivery receipt.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The carrier driver will not wait as you unpack and inspect the item unless there is visible damage to the package.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;When you sign the delivery receipt, the driver will leave.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Shipment Damage&lt;/b&gt;&lt;a name="2"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you see obvious damage to your shipment carton, you may ask the driver to open the carton and inspect the contents with you.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If upon inspection you find damage, you may refuse the shipment and write, "Refused, due to damage" on the delivery receipt. Keep a copy of the delivery receipt with your damage notations and contact Customer Care immediately.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Keep all packaging materials for 30 days to use in a return in case you discover damage or defects after delivery.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you discover damage or a defect after delivery, contact Customer Care. We will work to resolve the issue and, in our sole discretion, we may:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Arrange a repair or replacement if an item falls under a manufacturer's warranty;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Arrange for and pay the cost for repair of an item that does not fall under a manufacturer's warranty;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Issue a replacement; or Authorize a return&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Delivery sites&lt;/b&gt;&lt;a name="2"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Carriers deliver most fragile items only to the nearest ground-level entrance of your home, business, or residence.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Exceptions to the above policy include apartments, unusual driveways, or any other obstacles that impede delivery.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Prices and availability of products on our Site are subject to change without notice.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;All sales items are available only during the specified time-period, while they last, and under the specified terms.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Promotional sales may end with or without notice.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Upon termination of the sale or promotion, we are under no obligation, express or implied, to extend promotional sales terms or pricing.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;u&gt;Pricing Errors&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;We correct pricing errors when we discover them.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Incorrect prices sometimes appear on our Site, despite our best efforts.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;We normally verify prices as part of our dispatch procedures.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;When the correct price of a product is less than our stated price, we charge the lower amount when dispatching the product to you.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;When the correct price of a product is higher than our stated price, at our discretion, we will contact you for instructions before dispatching the order, or reject the order and notify you of such rejection.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;If a pricing error is reasonably obvious and unmistakable, we are under no obligation to provide the product to you at the incorrect (lower) price, even after we send you an Order Confirmation or Shipping Confirmation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Prices and availability of products on our Site are subject to change without notice.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;All sales items are available only during the specified time-period, while they last, and under the specified terms.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Promotional sales may end with or without notice.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Upon termination of the sale or promotion, we are under no obligation, express or implied, to extend promotional sales terms or pricing.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;u&gt;Pricing Errors&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;We correct pricing errors when we discover them.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Incorrect prices sometimes appear on our Site, despite our best efforts.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;We normally verify prices as part of our dispatch procedures.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;When the correct price of a product is less than our stated price, we charge the lower amount when dispatching the product to you.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;When the correct price of a product is higher than our stated price, at our discretion, we will contact you for instructions before dispatching the order, or reject the order and notify you of such rejection.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;If a pricing error is reasonably obvious and unmistakable, we are under no obligation to provide the product to you at the incorrect (lower) price, even after we send you an Order Confirmation or Shipping Confirmation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

