&lt;p&gt;Please note that although we allow no-hassle returns for personal fit items (clothing etc), we have restrictions on returns for items that provide an adjustable fit or are provided in a fixed standard size.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;At the time of writing, this includes the following items:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Watches&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Jewelry&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Scarves&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Purses&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Briefcases&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Wallets&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The restrictions on returns for these items are that the item will only be accepted in return (for a full refund - a 20% re-stocking fee) if the item is returned in its original packaging and/or with product tags intact.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You cannot change your order after submitting it.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You can place a different order if you cancel the original one.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;There is a short timeframe before your order reaches our warehouse for processing. You can cancel your order during that timeframe.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;If you cancel your order, contact your financial institution for your refund posting timeframe.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Please view our article on How to Cancel an Order for more information.&lt;/p&gt;
